      &#10060; Sredactedpless nights from relentless discomfort</span>
    </p>
    <p class="c0" style="height: 11pt; line-height: 1.15; orphans: 2; padding-bottom: 0pt; padding-top: 0pt; text-align: left; widows: 2; color: #000000; font-family: 'Arial'; font-size: 11pt; margin: 0;"></p>
    <p class="c1" style="line-height: 1.15; orphans: 2; padding-bottom: 0pt; padding-top: 0pt; text-align: left; widows: 2; color: #000000; font-family: 'Arial'; font-size: 11pt; margin: 0;">
      <span class="c3" style="color: #000000; font-family: 'Arial'; font-size: 11pt; font-style: normal; font-weight: 400; text-decoration: none; vertical-align: baseline;">You&rsquo;re not alone&mdash;millions suffer from unexplained nerve pain.</span>
    </p>
