    <p class="c1" style="line-height: 1.15; orphans: 2; padding-bottom: 0pt; padding-top: 0pt; text-align: left; widows: 2; color: #000000; font-family: 'Arial'; font-size: 11pt; margin: 0;">
      <span class="c3" style="color: #000000; font-family: 'Arial'; font-size: 11pt; font-style: normal; font-weight: 400; text-decoration: none; vertical-align: baseline;">But a new Johns Hopkins study may have just uncovered the real cause of nerve damage.</span>
    </p>
    <p class="c0" style="height: 11pt; line-height: 1.15; orphans: 2; padding-bottom: 0pt; padding-top: 0pt; text-align: left; widows: 2; color: #000000; font-family: 'Arial'; font-size: 11pt; margin: 0;"></p>
    <p class="c1" style="line-height: 1.15; orphans: 2; padding-bottom: 0pt; padding-top: 0pt; text-align: left; widows: 2; color: #000000; font-family: 'Arial'; font-size: 11pt; margin: 0;">
      <span>Researchers</span><span class="c11" style="font-weight: 700;">&nbsp;found that nerve deterioration isn&rsquo;t just &ldquo;random&rdquo; or a result of aging</span><span class="c3" style="color: #000000; font-family: 'Arial'; font-size: 11pt; font-style: normal; font-weight: 400; text-decoration: none; vertical-align: baseline;">. Instead, it&rsquo;s often triggered by a hidden biological process that&rsquo;s quietly damaging nerve endings&mdash;24/7.</span>
    </p>
    <p class="c0" style="height: 11pt; line-height: 1.15; orphans: 2; padding-bottom: 0pt; padding-top: 0pt; text-align: left; widows: 2; color: #000000; font-family: 'Arial'; font-size: 11pt; margin: 0;"></p>
    <p class="c1" style="line-height: 1.15; orphans: 2; padding-bottom: 0pt; padding-top: 0pt; text-align: left; widows: 2; color: #000000; font-family: 'Arial'; font-size: 11pt; margin: 0;">
      <span class="c11" style="font-weight: 700;">The good news?</span><span class="c3" style="color: #000000; font-family: 'Arial'; font-size: 11pt; font-style: normal; font-weight: 400; text-decoration: none; vertical-align: baseline;">&nbsp;A breakthrough method has been found to stop this process, repair fragile nerves, and restore sensation&mdash;in just a few seconds per day.</span>
    </p>
    <p class="c0" style="height: 11pt; line-height: 1.15; orphans: 2; padding-bottom: 0pt; padding-top: 0pt; text-align: left; widows: 2; color: #000000; font-family: 'Arial'; font-size: 11pt; margin: 0;"></p>
    <p class="c1" style="line-height: 1.15; orphans: 2; padding-bottom: 0pt; padding-top: 0pt; text-align: left; widows: 2; color: #000000; font-family: 'Arial'; font-size: 11pt; margin: 0;">
      <span class="c3" style="color: #000000; font-family: 'Arial'; font-size: 11pt; font-style: normal; font-weight: 400; text-decoration: none; vertical-align: baseline;">People who have suffered for years are already reporting:</span>
    </p>
    <p class="c1" style="line-height: 1.15; orphans: 2; padding-bottom: 0pt; padding-top: 0pt; text-align: left; widows: 2; color: #000000; font-family: 'Arial'; font-size: 11pt; margin: 0;">
      <span><br></span><span class="c2" style="color: #000000; font-family: 'Arial'; font-size: 11pt; font-style: normal; font-weight: 700; text-decoration: none; vertical-align: baseline;">&#10004; Pain relief and reduced numbness<br>
      &#10004; Restored nerve function and improved mobility<br>
      &#10004; A return to normal life&mdash;without invasive treatments</span>
    </p>
    <p class="c0" style="height: 11pt; line-height: 1.15; orphans: 2; padding-bottom: 0pt; padding-top: 0pt; text-align: left; widows: 2; color: #000000; font-family: 'Arial'; font-size: 11pt; margin: 0;"></p>
    <p class="c1" style="line-height: 1.15; orphans: 2; padding-bottom: 0pt; padding-top: 0pt; text-align: left; widows: 2; color: #000000; font-family: 'Arial'; font-size: 11pt; margin: 0;">
      <span class="c3" style="color: #000000; font-family: 'Arial'; font-size: 11pt; font-style: normal; font-weight: 400; text-decoration: none; vertical-align: baseline;">If you&rsquo;ve been told there&rsquo;s nothing you can do, this changes everything.</span>
    </p>
